author: Warhammer
description:
Alongside today's release of the Hive Scum class, Fatshark is releasing the free update No Man's Land! Experience trench warfare under the open sky as you play the all new operation set on the fringes of Tertium. 
The new No Man's Land operation is the final part of a story campaign consisting of three missions with a connected storyline.

The update also contains: 
A new Ogryn personality 
New live event: Atonement which will go live December 4. 
New regimental bundle: Athonian Tunnel Rats 
Quality of Life and balancing changes 

Find out more about all the content available in the update! 
https://fatshark.games/An5dqw
